It is the 6th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|å­ååđēæŊ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Boshin|ja|æčū°|1=Yang Earth Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Boshin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Boshin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Earth Dragon|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Kougo|ja|åšå|1=Yang Metal Horse|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kougo|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kougo|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Metal Horse|qq=}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|é°é―äščĄææģ|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|ååđē|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Ki|ja|å·ą|1=Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|lt=Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|2=ja|3=å·ą|4=zh|5=å·ą|1=Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (å·ą)|qq=}} represents yin {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (å)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|zh|Earth (å)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (å)|2=ru|3=ÐÐĩÐžÐŧŅ (Ņ-ŅÐļÐ―)|4=mn|5=ÐĻÐūŅÐūÐū (ÐžÐ°ŅÐąÐūÐī)|6=uk|7=ÐÐĩÐžÐŧŅ (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|8=als|9=Ãrde in dr chinesische FÃžmf-ElemÃĪnt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Tháŧ (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (å)|2=ru|3=ÐÐĩÐžÐŧŅ (Ņ-ŅÐļÐ―)|4=mn|5=ÐĻÐūŅÐūÐū (ÐžÐ°ŅÐąÐūÐī)|6=uk|7=ÐÐĩÐžÐŧŅ (ÐĢ-ŅŅÐ―)|8=als|9=Ãrde in dr chinesische FÃžmf-ElemÃĪnt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Tháŧ (NgÅĐ hÃ nh)|